WEBVTT

00:00:58.413 --> 00:01:01.851
O dikwa m k'ajuru m aju.

00:01:03.139 --> 00:01:05.498
E nwerem ezinulo huru m n'anya nke ukwu

00:01:05.522 --> 00:01:07.829
na ndi enyi m tukwasara obi,

00:01:07.853 --> 00:01:12.422
na agbanyeghi ya, ekweghi m
agwa onye obula,

00:01:12.446 --> 00:01:14.476
gbasara ihe mgbu m.

00:01:16.004 --> 00:01:20.471
O dikwam k'onweghi ihe m puru ime
n'ihi omenala anyi n'Africa,

00:01:20.495 --> 00:01:22.785
gbasara obi isi ike nwoke kwesiri inwe.

00:01:22.785 --> 00:01:24.406
"Ndi nmadu na enwe nsogbu,Sangu.

00:01:25.936 --> 00:01:27.000
Nagide onwe gi"

00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:30.424
Oge mbu m nuru maka "isi izu oke,"